Welcome to HorizonWorks! This checklist will help you get your technology 
set up on Day 1.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
BEFORE YOUR FIRST DAY
------------------------------------------------------------------------

[ ] Check your personal email for HorizonWorks IT welcome message
[ ] Note your temporary password (expires after first login)
[ ] Download required apps on your phone (see list below)

------------------------------------------------------------------------
DAY 1 SETUP TASKS
------------------------------------------------------------------------

LAPTOP SETUP:
[ ] Receive laptop from IT (MacBook Pro or Dell XPS based on role)
[ ] Power on and complete initial macOS/Windows setup
[ ] Connect to "HorizonWorks-Guest" WiFi for initial setup
[ ] Sign in with your @horizonworks.com credentials
[ ] Complete automatic software installation (takes ~30 minutes)
[ ] Restart when prompted
[ ] Connect to "HorizonWorks-Secure" WiFi with your credentials

ACCOUNTS TO SET UP:
[ ] Gmail (for HorizonWorks email)
[ ] Slack
[ ] Okta (for SSO)
[ ] 1Password (password manager)
[ ] Zoom
[ ] Jira
[ ] Confluence

VPN SETUP:
[ ] Download Cisco AnyConnect from Software Center
[ ] Connect to vpn.horizonworks.com
[ ] Use your Okta credentials
[ ] Complete MFA enrollment (phone or hardware key)

PHONE APPS:
[ ] Slack
[ ] Okta Verify (for MFA)
[ ] Gmail
[ ] Zoom

