------------------------------------------------------------------------
COMMON ISSUES & SOLUTIONS
------------------------------------------------------------------------

"Laptop won't connect to WiFi"
→ Ensure you're connecting to HorizonWorks-Secure, not Guest
→ Verify caps lock is off when entering password

"Can't access internal websites"
→ Make sure VPN is connected (check AnyConnect icon)
→ Try disconnecting and reconnecting

"Okta login failing"
→ Clear browser cache
→ Try incognito/private window
→ Contact IT if persists

